@deffn {Function} getenv (@var{env})
Get the value of the environmentvariable @var{env}

Example:

@example
(%i1) load("operatingsystem")$
(%i2) getenv("PATH");
(%o2) /usr/local/sbin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/sbin:/usr/bin:/sbin:/bin
@end example

@end deffn



